title: Prepar3d v1.4 complete with crack
description:
I downloaded Prepar3d v1.4 and a crack that was given on another torrent. I decided to package it in all one download so others would not have to locate the crack to run it. I've tested it in Windows 7 x64 and it works completely with the crack. Instructions are included inside the rar file.

Enjoy....and buy it if you can afford it.  It runs better than FSX on my system so I hope it works better for you.
